Amanda's many accomplishments

00:04:23.820 --> 00:04:26.250
in your program, or
talk to her grandmother.

00:04:26.250 --> 00:04:31.780
And tonight we have the privilege

00:04:31.780 --> 00:04:35.480
to hear Amanda read a poem
she's composed especially

00:04:35.480 --> 00:04:36.780
for this occasion.

00:04:36.780 --> 00:04:39.470
So please join me in
welcoming Amanda Gorman,

00:04:39.470 --> 00:04:42.510
the nation's first
youth poet laureate.

00:04:42.510 --> 00:04:57.790
[ Applause ]

00:04:57.790 --> 00:05:02.040
&gt;&gt; Amanda Gorman: Amanda,
center yourself, get ready.

00:05:02.040 --> 00:05:06.430
Before I read my poem, I want to
give my most sincere thank you

00:05:06.430 --> 00:05:10.570
