prize-winning poetry collection,

00:11:12.920 --> 00:11:16.630
Life on Mars, and I was wowed.

00:11:16.630 --> 00:11:22.260 position:56%
In poem such as My God, it's Full of
Stars, the Speed of Belief, and Yes,

00:11:22.260 --> 00:11:27.580
Life on Mars, Tracy takes us
farther than we imagine we can go,

00:11:27.580 --> 00:11:31.620
to the great beyond and
deeply inward as well.

00:11:31.620 --> 00:11:35.230
Her poems walk us through
their wandering.

00:11:35.230 --> 00:11:39.580 position:56%
Their power is that they can go
anywhere they want: scientific fact,

00:11:39.580 --> 00:11:43.770
