memories, and arguments of faith.

00:11:43.770 --> 00:11:48.350
They aren't simple
but they are direct.

00:11:48.350 --> 00:11:50.850
And they aren't afraid
to face the painful parts

00:11:50.850 --> 00:11:53.110
