00:11:53.110 --> 00:11:58.310
My favorite moment in the book
came in the poem, They may love all

00:11:58.310 --> 00:12:02.550
that he has chosen and hate
all that he has rejected.

00:12:02.550 --> 00:12:07.580 position:56%
While the title dates back more than
2000 years to the Dead Sea Scrolls,

00:12:07.580 --> 00:12:10.460
