for lack of what is found there.

00:12:41.680 --> 00:12:46.500
Our great American poet and
newest poet laureate knows how

00:12:46.500 --> 00:12:50.940
to give us the news our minds
and hearts and souls most need.

00:12:50.940 --> 00:12:55.510
