with the body.

00:18:13.920 --> 00:18:17.890
When you close your eyes,
I know you are listening

00:18:17.890 --> 00:18:21.290
to a dark chamber around
a chord of light.

00:18:21.290 --> 00:18:27.140
I know you are deciding
that the body's a question:

00:18:27.140 --> 00:18:30.130
What do you believe in?

00:18:33.100 --> 00:18:39.570
It will rain tomorrow, as it rained
in the dark days after you died.

00:18:39.570 --> 00:18:43.990
And I will struggle with what
to wear, and take a place

00:18:43.990 --> 00:18:47.780
